Okay, let's break this down systematically. The user wants the new administrative unit for "Xã Đông Minh, Huyện Tiền Hải, Tỉnh Thái Bình". My process involves cross-referencing resolutions and data.

First, I need to address the provincial change. I know that the old province "Tỉnh Thái Bình" has merged. According to Resolution 60-NQ/TW, it has become part of "Tỉnh Hưng Yên". So, "Tỉnh Thái Bình" effectively no longer exists in this context.
